The following is the schedule time for the Classic from Tuesday’s first round until the final day on Friday, March 26: 

Tuesday- Day One- March 23, 2021- Live schedule from Karen on SuperSport Golf (DStv Channel 233 from 12.00, ending at 15.00; 

Wednesday- Day Two- March 24, 2021- Live Schedule from Karen on SuperSport Golf (DStv 233) from 12.00 ending at 15.00. 

Thursday- Day Three- March 25, 2021- Live Schedule from Karen- SuperSport Golf (DStv 233) from 11.30 ending 14.30. 

Friday- Day Four- March 26, 2021-Live from Schedule from Karen- SuperSport Golf (DStv channel 233 from 11.30 ending 14.30. 

